Field.Description: The rule is a Role specified in an Access Token.

Field.Name: AuthenticatedUser
Field.Description: The rule specifies any non Anonymous UserIdentityToken.

Field.Description: The rule specifies the combination of an application identity and an Anonymous UserIdentityToken.
